    public abstract class AbstractCollQuery<Q extends AbstractCollQuery<Q>>
extends ProjectableQuery<Q>
implements SimpleQuery<Q>
    AbstractCollQuery provides a base class for Collection query implementations. Extend it like this 
     public class MyType extends AbstractColQuery<MyType>{
